name: MyTea
0:
”Alexa, ask My Tea what is in Jasmine”
”Alexa, ask My Tea what has Cinnamon”
”Alexa, ask My Tea what's in English Breakfast”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my tea
des:
This is for use with Dot or Echo. This skill is used to learn more about what is in the tea that you drink. You can ask that is in Earl Grey Tea or it you have a particular ingredient such as Cinnamon, you can learn what common tea has that ingredient.

This will help the public learn more about tea and what is in the tea they are drinking.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
